'''Faye Daniels''' is the judge who presided over [[Katie Kent|Katie Kent's]] hearing.

==History==
Faye was assigned to preside over Katie's trial. When Violet was being sworn in, Faye reminded her that she needed to say, "I do." but Violet left, saying she couldn't do it.

She also presided when Violet testified about her point of view on the attack and that she believed that Katie was delusional during the attack.

==Career==
She is a judge in Los Angeles.
